<div class="container">
  <h1 class="text-center my-16 font-bold text-4xl">The home of the Portfolio tracker</h1>
  <div><%= image_tag 'portfolio_tracker.jpg', class:"mx-auto" %></div>
  <div class="my-24">
    <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-6">Finally, a portfolio tracker you dreamed about! Track your investments in real time.</p>
    <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-6">Keep a track of your realized profit/loss from each stock.</p>
    <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-center">See you Net Worth moving, stay informed.</p>
    <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8 mt-12">Portfolios page</p>
    <%= image_tag 'ex_1.png', class:"w-3/4 mx-auto mb-12 mt-8" %>
    <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8 mt-12">Company news page</p>
    <%= image_tag 'ex_3.png', class:"w-3/4 mx-auto mb-12 mt-8" %>
    <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8 mt-12">Transactions page</p>
    <%= image_tag 'ex_5.png', class:"w-3/4 mx-auto mb-12 mt-8" %>
    
  </div>
  <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">Join the club and get control over your investments.</p>
  <div class="flex container w-full mt-24 gap-x-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col content-center">
      <div><%= image_tag 'portfolio1.jpg', class:"rounded-full" %></div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-center my-4">Real time portfolio tracking</h2>
      <p class="text-center">Record all your transactions and watch your portfolio performance in real time. It gives you detailed individual stock and total portfolio value, daily profit/loss, percentage profit/loss, realized profit/loss and transactions cost.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-col content-center">
      <div><%= image_tag 'portfolio2.jpg', class:"rounded-full" %></div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-center my-4">Track all of your investments</h2>
      <p class="text-center">You can create multiple portfolios and track the investements per each portfolio, but also have the big picture. See your total Net Worth. What is your gain today as a dollar value and as a percentage. </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div><%= image_tag 'portfolio3.jpg', class:"rounded-full" %></div>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-center my-4">Research, information, news</h2>
      <p class="text-center">Get detailed information about your portfolio stocks (US market only). Read the latest company news and announcements, look for the insider tradings and the company's earnings surprises. </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mt-24">Hurry up and register until it's still free.</p>
  <div class="mt-24 flex container">
    <div class="flex justify-around">
      <div class="flex flex-col w-1/5 items-center">
        <%
=begin%>
 <div><%= image_tag 'sign_up', class:"rounded-full mb-12" %></div> 
<%
=end%>
        <div><%= link_to 'So, sign up now', new_user_registration_path, class:"text-center text-3xl font-bold text-dollar hover:text-dollar-darker" %></div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col w-1/5 items-center">
        <div><%= image_tag 'sign_in', class:"rounded-full mb-12" %></div>
        <div><%= link_to 'Or simply login', new_user_session_path, class:"text-center text-3xl font-bold text-dollar hover:text-dollar-darker" %></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="my-16 flex-col container content-center">
    <p class="text-center text-3xl font-bold text-dollar">Because did I say ...</p>
    <div><%= image_tag 'free', class:" w-1/4 mx-auto mt-12" %></div>
  </div>
</div>
